Installation ver 0.2
====================
1) Download and install gSOAP, http://gsoap2.sourceforge.net and Graphviz,
   http://www.graphviz.org
   The things needed from bashlib (http://bashlib.sourceforge.net) and 
   Tigra Tree Menu (http://www.softcomplex.com/products/tigra_tree_menu)
   are included in this distribution.
2) edit the first section of install_wflow.sh to conform to your site
3) run install_wflow.sh as root

notes
=====
OS X: dot in Graphviz.app is located in Graphviz.app/Contents/MacOS/dot, so make
      a link from there to /usr/bin/dot
